---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About TendersMW | Malawi Procurement Intelligence"
  description="TendersMW aggregates government and development tenders from across Malawi into one searchable platform."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text mb-6">About TendersMW</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-muted">
      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">What We Do</h2>
        <p>TendersMW is Malawi's procurement intelligence platform. We aggregate government tenders, procurement notices, and contract opportunities from multiple sources into one searchable directory.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Instead of checking PPDA, MANEPS, World Bank, African Development Bank, and UN procurement portals separately, you can find everything here.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Our Sources</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><strong class="text-text">PPDA</strong> — Public Procurement and Disposal of Assets Authority</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">MANEPS</strong> — Malawi National Electronic Procurement System</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">World Bank</strong> — International development project procurement</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">African Development Bank</strong> — AfDB-funded procurement notices</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">EU TED</strong> — European Union Tenders Electronic Daily</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">UNGM</strong> — United Nations Global Marketplace</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">ESCOM</strong> — Electricity Supply Corporation of Malawi</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">MRA</strong> — Malawi Revenue Authority</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Who We Serve</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><strong class="text-text">Malawian businesses</strong> looking for government and development project opportunities</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">International companies</strong> seeking procurement opportunities in Malawi</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">NGOs and development organizations</strong> tracking procurement in the country</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text">Researchers and journalists</strong> analyzing public procurement patterns</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-sm">TendersMW is an aggregation service. We collect and present tender information from publicly available sources. We do not issue, manage, or adjudicate tenders. Always verify tender details directly with the procuring entity before submitting a bid. We make every effort to ensure accuracy but cannot guarantee that all information is complete or up-to-date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
